> > | still present in 2.6.23-rc6. To reproduce
> > |
> > | swapoff -a
> > | echo disk > /sys/power/state
> > | echo disk > /sys/power/state
> > |
> > | Unsetting
> > |
> > | CONFIG_IEEE1394=y
> > |
> > | solves the problem.
